    <h1>About Me</h1>
    <hr/>
    <p>
        I'm Miquilina Junior, I live in Rotherhithe, London. I have 
        three children, Anderson, Kelly and Alison. I have 7 years
        experience. Five within a nuursey setting and two as a 
        registered childminder. I am registered to care for 6 children. 
        Thats broken down to 1 baby and a mix of five children either
        under 5 or over. At my Ofsted inspection I recieved "GOOD" grading.
        <br/><br>
        I take my chosen occupation very seriously and try to take any
        steps which I feel will increase my effectiveness as a 
        Registered Childminder and improve the service I provide.
        Therefore, I am always keen to update and refresh my knowledge
        through relevant training courses. I have completed a Level 3
        qualification "Childcare".
    </p>
    
    
