    <section id="Setting">
        <h1 id="Setting-anchor">The Setting</h1>
        <hr/>
        <p>
            Your child will be cared for in a home-like
            environment within a family atmosphere.  
            They will receive individual attention whilst 
            also enjoying interaction with children of 
            various ages. I attend regular sessions at 
            Toddler groups and soft play centres. When we 
            can, we spend as much time out of the house as 
            possible, visiting places such as the library
            and park. WE also do activities within the setting,
            such as painting and other types of creative activities 
            where the children can take an active role in what they want 
            to do within a selection. As i have a garden there are also 
            outdoor activities at the setting for the children. Such as Sand play, 
            water play and variety of other outdoor toys. 
            <br><br>
            Incase of an emergency where im not available, 
            I work alongside another childminder, Patricia
            who lives very close at flat 8. This a requirement 
            from Ofsted that as a childminder i need to know another 
            registered childminder incase of emergencies. 

            </p>
